---
title: Squash, Bacon and Chicken Breast Alfredo with Fried Sage Leaves
description: This luscious linguine dish is extra comforting and cozy! Everyone loves alfredo, and this one gets a seasonal spin with smoky bacon, sweet squash and savoury sage. You'll be licking the plate clean!
